this_title: The Last Supper: A Sopranos Session
introduction: The Last Supper: A Sopranos Session invites you to join Vincent Pastore, Federico Castelluccio, Vincent Curatola and Arthur J. Nascarella for an intimate dinner at Il Cortile, in Little Italy, the restaurant cast members would go to for a commiseration dinner after their characters were killed off the show. In this five course conversation the cast talks about their craft, the life and grind of working on a series and their extraordinary twenty year journey on The Sopranos.
